metadata.name: LOVE
metadata.description:
Love is not a fall

Not a rush

Not for the first sight

Not for the weak

Love is never for the lier


Love is an inner communication 

An observation between heart and mind 

A powerful reflection between two souls floating in the universe feeling and thinking on the same level

Love is not a mistake

Love should never bring pain and tears

Love is power and for that love â€‹is only for the strongest 

For the honest

For the real ... and real is rare

And once it's found .. we shine 


__________________

A digital piece | 2021
